        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="Snowball"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="snow"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="winter"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="ball"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    
                    <l> I made myself a snowball</l>
                    <l> As perfect as could be.</l>
                    <l>I thought I'd keep it as a pet</l>
                    <l> And let it sleep with me.</l>
                    <l> I made it some pajamas</l>
                    <l> And a pillow for its head.</l>
                    <l>Then last night it ran away,</l>
                    <l> But first it wet the bed.</l>
                    
                    
                    
                    <l> Source: https://www.familyfriendpoems.com/poem/snowball-by-shel-silverstein</l>
